---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Dog-Friendly Hotels in London — A Dog's Guide"
description: "The best dog-friendly hotels in London, grouped by area and rated on the Golden Paw Scale."
footerType: london
permalink: /london/hotels/
---

<div class="dest-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="dest-breadcrumb">
      <a href="/london/"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></i> London</a>
      <span>›</span> Hotels
    </p>
    <h1>Hotels</h1>
    <p class="dest-intro-desc">Independently verified — fees, size limits and dog policies confirmed before we publish.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="venue-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Browse by area</p>
      <h2>Areas</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="venue-list">
      {% for item in london_hotels %}
      <a href="/london/hotels/{{ item.slug }}/" class="dest-subpage-card">
        <div class="dest-subpage-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h3>{{ item.area }}</h3>
        <span class="dest-card-link">View</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
